						<summary>

						<p>This is the same as No. 528 of 1905 with the built in portion at the end cleared. It records a gift of 30 <hi rend="italic">kaḻañju</hi> of gold for a perpetual lamp in the temple of Tiruvānaikkal-Perumānaḍigaḷ at Tiruveḷḷaṟai by <hi rend="bold">Araiyaṉ Tāḻi</hi> of the same village.</p>						

						</summary>
